Images: ["[630_360_16832...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/thumb_files/630_360_1683293537-468.jpg)", "[1683293536-29...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/1683293536-293.jpg)", "[1683293536-13...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/1683293536-137.jpg)", "[1683293536-25...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/1683293536-255.jpg)"]

